Quickstrike:




Quickstrike was pacing down the hall. He found himself doing it more 
when he was nervous or bored. It was becoming a habit now. He 
grumbled to himself as he went down. He wasn't happy with Hell Beast 
around. He wasn't going to calm down until something was done about 
him. He didn't get why he was here. He claimed that he was leader of 
the Predacons, but he had that all wrong. Black Arachnia was.

He forced himself to stop pacing and went to find Tarantulas, his old 
partner. "Hey T," he called. He sighed while looking for him. "Ah 
don't get it." he said low, hardly loud enough to be heard.
